  "siteName": "逛逛GitHub",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=590e7e5b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePw3ZeGRruwv7hpO0KQLqkVyCtn8tNgae65K9AA2TOKm2paXQ8acAYVILkS3FwibNUCTiclly0JTqdMMaKLkV60A%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <ms-text-chunk data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <ms-cmark-node>\n    <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"逛逛GitHub\" data-alias=\"ggGithub\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ePw3ZeGRruyXo8VzACicO8MVibibicuJUQ8Vzghx6WF8F51breYjBIuYd4cj6wp26BYrg850bNuA20rdic9UyKIUhpg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"热门「开源项目」推送到你眼前，每日为你节省 1 小时。 给我发消息可咨询各种开源项目，专注 AI、硬科技开源领域。\" data-id=\"MzUxNjg4NDEzNA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wfhlc\">这是一个非常有意思的 GitHub 开源项目，名叫 MiroFish。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1jud\">刚开源没多长时间，已经有 1000 多人 Star 了。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1crm\">它是一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">基于多智能体技术的预测引擎，通过模拟群体行为来推演未来。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6185185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100046923\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=952bf648&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruwv7hpO0KQLqkVyCtn8tNgaYh2AfZYicmDnnJLOiayP5AicXNOrjJHoIAHxUWvZawHJ8vSJz1LTXSD7A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf18p1\">啥意思呢？&nbsp;</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1ubr\">你给它一些现实世界的种子信息，比如某一个突发事件的描述。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wftjw\">它会基于这些信息，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">自动构建一个高保真的平行数字世界。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1mek\">在这个数字空间里，成千上万个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;AI 智能体拥有独立的人格、长期的记忆和行为逻辑</span>。它们会像真实世界的人一样自由交互，进行社会演化。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wfrhc\">使用者可以站在上帝视角，动态注入变量，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">观察事情会如何发展。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1t7j\">也就是这：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-style: italic;text-decoration: underline;\">上传任意报告，即刻推演未来。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5648148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100046924\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0bc6c2d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruwv7hpO0KQLqkVyCtn8tNga6YMcaqpPYRKDc4RDUmT9CTTffDp4oQ0rXwrpMFnfmZWG9IMiaKuM6Gg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\">开源地址：<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">https</span>:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//github.com/666ghj/MiroFish</span></span></code></pre>\n    <p></p>\n    <p class=\"js_darkmode__14\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: Futura-Medium;font-size: 32px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">01</span></span></p>\n    <p class=\"js_darkmode__15\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 16px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong class=\"js_darkmode__16\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">开源项目简介</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf11lm\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">还记得之前逛逛推荐的开源项目&nbsp;</span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">BettaFish 吗？</span></span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <h1 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1ec5\">就是那个&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUxNjg4NDEzNA==&amp;mid=2247528548&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=83a34b20b4e54768f7b6d7f5e4d41542&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"1 天狂揽 4000 多 Star 的 AI 舆情分析开源神器\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">1 天狂揽 4000 多 Star 的 AI 舆情分析开源神器</a>。</span></h1>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf243b\">这个叫 MiroFish 就是开发者另外一个开源项目。它的理念还是挺有意思的，可以先看看这个介绍视频：</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf239r\">可以看到，MiroFish 的工作流程分为几步：</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf9ur\">首先是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">图谱构建</span>，提取信息并注入记忆；然后是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">环境搭建</span>，生成人设和配置环境。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1r78\">接着<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">开始模拟</span>，双平台并行运行，动态更新记忆；最后由专门的报告<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">智能体生成结果</span>。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5972222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100046928\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32b608c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruwv7hpO0KQLqkVyCtn8tNgaiare5H9tgwR1U5MWfHlO6UpCn3MIFicfyPqMv6TRKnwyUtwKStzW4xTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wfq55\">MiroFish 采用了增强版的时序 GraphRAG 技术来构建知识图谱，能处理具有先后顺序的复杂记忆，从而精准还原事件背景。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkbad5wf1era\">系统会自动<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">为每个 Agent 设定详细的人格属性、记忆背景，</span>甚至包括其在社交媒体上的活跃时间段。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-